title: Why So Blue?

title: Behind the Curtain: Steven Universe the Movie
description: This documentary follows Rebecca Sugar and the Crewniverse as they lead the audience on the journey of creating Steven Universe the Movie. From Cartoon Network Studios to Zuma Beach, the fans get an in-depth look at the formation of the story, the process of writing the music, and the collaboration between musicians, the Crewniverse, and the cast, while experiencing the locations where they took place.

description: Change (feat. Zach Callison) - From Steven Universe The Movie.

title: A Very Special Episode
description: Rainbow Quartz 2.0 promised to hang out with Onion the same day Sunstone scheduled a home safety Geminar! How can Steven be in two places, and two fusions, at once?
